        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "Honestly, A correction is a reliability signal, not a failure. We've seen this play out at teams using BBC. If you ignore that, you end up rebuilding it from scratch a year later.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 30000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 24000,
